{
  "stem": "21482.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I think that my mother and I would-- we'd never work on the same shift in the beginning together, for whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my father had an awful lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody liked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just could do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in, in the family that, that came to ghetto, like my father's family, brothers, and sisters-in-law, he was a-- and my grandparents, my mother's parents, and my mother younger sister, he was able to help us-- help a lot when they were being-- when every few months, you had to go and get another permit to remain.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was able to get permits for, for other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then one of my uncle became-- my father and one of my uncles became members of the Ordnungsdienst, the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Marcel Goldberg, my father arranged for him to become a police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I think they had clout.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could arrange things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew a little ahead of time when the Germans were coming, when there would be, you know, when, when there be another selection.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would protect people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for, for a few months, I think that they were able to help themselves and a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, one time, one of my girlfriend's mother was being taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came right-- came to my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went to help her and get her back, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a few months later, she went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the same thing happened with my grandparents, my mother's parents, that first few selections, my father was able to save them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one selection, my father didn't get a, a permit.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
